[t7.A_Creature_champion_sanctuary H7Creature]
mName="Unagi"
mLore="When news of the sudden attacks and the disappearance of civilians started to come from the lakeside Shanria villages, worried daimyos sent several armed squads there to clarify the situation. The interviewed villagers claimed to have been the victims of the insidious ningyos - river monsters from local legends, so the Naga scouts decided to explore the network of underground rivers and lakes under the Dragon Causeway. There they were attacked by mysterious creatures and were able to avoid death only thanks to the timely appearance of the Ocean Guards who lived in that area. Some time passed before the Naga managed to establish contact with the "lesser horrors of the deep", but to this day the inhabitants of Shanria are wary of these unpredictable underwater creatures, whose long dresses hide toothy eels that serve as their lower limbs."

