[t7.A_Creature_champion_Sanctuary_upregate H7Creature]
mName="Denki Unagi"
mLore="Officially, Unagi are considered to be the Mermaids, whose bodies and minds were distorted under the influence of the blood of the Dragon God of Chaos seeped into the water. Although, there exist some unusual theories, such as the one where the eels consists the main body, and the humanoid form serves only as a bait for careless victims. Cunning and vindictive by nature, they feel no remorse for their actions on the battlefield, drawing strength even from the fear and disgust of their own allies. If the wounded Denki Unagi do not have the opportunity to take revenge on the offenders for the wounds they received, then they vent their rage on everyone around them, not caring about who is friend and who is foe."

